{"tid":879544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚮台灣旅行中，食左人地的kfc.","createTime":"2018-10-28T05:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:35:57.000Z","uid":120123,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1258cf866722c68c2dfeb268d6e878214a054a","tid":879544,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:04:03.000Z","msg":"個雞皇飯正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n人地d雞皇飯真係入味。香港果d求撚其比d白飯你，然後撈pat汁落去。<br />\n台灣果d真係整到好似油飯咁，有味，但係表面無汁。<br />\n人地d特別雞 （呢期係紙包雞) 真係有特別整法同入味。香港d特別雞只係改變左隻雞表面d味粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，我見人地出面d鋪頭都有賣飲管，即係呢樣野可能人地都興。<br />\n但係人地餐廳唔會逼客人唔用飲管。但係人地垃圾回收係有分類。係咁樣去做環保。<br />\n香港環保撚收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c03ca5857d80ef7f634775ade488ed09216f26","tid":879544,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"a541df17c113bbd98e602cb11d29f9c384790a3a","tid":879544,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"以為kfc = 台雞"},{"pid":"d14f0e77cb5cb2b62e5534b2ad57fcc2e8c4690d","tid":879544,"uid":199415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"香港人除左識自己人踩自己人仲識d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0033f3a7300613661fa33883e18cc1a56b705240","tid":879544,"uid":171555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14f0e77cb5cb2b62e5534b2ad57fcc2e8c4690d","tid":879544,"uid":199415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"香港人除左識自己人踩自己人仲識d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"事實 香港kfc係特別難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b3859477d28d257860fb3576b3894861c8b472","tid":879544,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo